ible performance from Elouan Gardon!#ParisParalympicspic.twitter.com/dJDaCeBMOI Veteran teammate Bryan Larsen (Windsor, California) spotted Gardon's talent as a road rider and encouraged him to pursuepara-cycling.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 904, \"end\": 909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.8535265909252858, \"rank\": 0.16949806676541046, \"text\": \"Bryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Bryan\"}, {\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Windsor,_California\", \"score\": 0.9999999999947704, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Windsor, California\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Windsor,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Windsor,_California\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The youngest member\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"his Paralympic debut!Incredible performance\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 820}, {\"ngram\": \"Gardon's talent\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"a road rider\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"pursuepara-cycling\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After receiving an invitation to a talent identification camp in June, it became evident that Gardon possessed untapped potential, officials said.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an invitation\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"a talent identification camp\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"Gardon\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"untapped potential\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Larsen also took to the track, competing in the men's 4000m C4 individual pursuit race opposite Team France, where the rowdy home crowds did not rattle Larsen.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_France\", \"score\": 0.8336437903501275, \"rank\": 0.19817451264241645, \"text\": \"Team France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A1_Team_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Larsen\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 4000m C4 individual pursuit race\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"the rowdy home crowds\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1306}, {\"ngram\": \"Larsen\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was almost numbing to a certain degree, it was almost better,\\\" Larsen said.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a certain degree\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"Larsen\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because it was so loud, it almost drowned my own thoughts, which sometimes negative thoughts can creep in.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my own thoughts\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1469}, {\"ngram\": \"sometimes negative thoughts\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really, really happy to be able to subconsciously stick to my habits.\\\"\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my habits\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Larsen beat his own national record by nearly a full second, a time he had previously set in March at the 2024 UCI Para-Cycling World Championships, but that was not enough to reach the medal round.\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1708, \"end\": 1711, \"title\": \"http